/-
In this file, we define notation `X^n` to take powers of types.
By definition, `X^n` is modelled as functions from `fin n` to `X`.
-/

/-- A definition of powers of a type. -/
def type_pow : has_pow (Type*) ℕ := ⟨λ A n, fin n → A⟩


